description:
LinkAdaptation:  Table storing link adaptation parameters for individual cells, identified by timestamp, area, cell ID, and various identifiers.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the link adaptation record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
- Id2: Redundant/alternative cell identifier.
- Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely internal).
- Id4: Unknown identifier (likely internal).
- vsDataType: Data type indicator specifying the data as link adaptation information.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific attributes format.
- LinkAdaptation.linkAdaptationId: Unique identifier for the specific link adaptation configuration.
